Power, the U.S. ambassador,
called for more

13:57.403 --> 13:59.205 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
sanctions.

13:59.238 --> 14:03.476 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And many candidates today who
