intended to do?

16:20.613 --> 16:23.616 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WENDY SHERMAN: Well, I think
he's -- it's
several things.

16:23.649 --> 16:29.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First of all, it's really to
bring together
his own country to believe that
he is strong

16:29.155 --> 16:33.826 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
